This is a page for gathering resources and info concerning translations in English. Click on Edit to add content. You can also create subpages as explained in the [Creating or linking to other pages within the wiki](https://share.coursera.org/wiki/index.php/Help:Editing#Creating_or_linking_to_other_pages_within_the_wiki) section of the [[Help:Editing]] page.


NB This subpage is not really needed presently, as the subtitles the GTC translates are all in English. But it might be of use if Coursera adds subtitles of videos in other languages in future.
